  schema:name "Methods of Cybernetic-Postliberal Analysis" ;
  schema:description "How to perform cybernetic-postliberal analysis on a specific case, organized around five operative questions: what structural contradiction is being metabolized, what genres are operating, what feedback loops are running, where the metabolism lands, what the case admits and refuses. With the reflexive corollary that the school is itself a metabolizable subject-position." ;
